
'''''Cook Off''''' ni filime yo gusetsa y'urukundo yo muri [[Zimbabwe]] yasohotse muri 2017 yanditswe kandi iyoborwa na Tomas Brickhill <ref>https://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/english/cook-off</ref>.  film ikinamo Tendaiishe Chitima, Fungai Majaya na Tehn Diamond<ref>https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/may/31/cook-off-the-no-budget-romcom-that-became-the-first-zimbabwean-film-on-netflix</ref> .  Gutunganya iyi filime byahoraga byibasirwa no kunanirwa kw'amashanyarazi, imbogamizi z’ingengo y’imari, imyigaragambyo yo kurwanya leta n’imvururu zadutse mu cyiciro cya nyuma cya Perezidansi ya Robert Mugabe<ref>https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-52983564</ref> . Yabaye filime ya mbere yasohotse muri Zimbabwe nyuma ya Mugabe yamaze imyaka igera kuri 40<ref>https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/cook-off</ref>.  Iyi filime kandi yabaye filime ya mbere ya Zimbabwe yerekanwe kuri Netflix .   Yitabiriwe n’itangazamakuru mpuzamahanga kuva yashyirwa ku rubuga rwa Netflix muri Kamena 2020<ref>https://thetimesofafrica.com/8000-romcom-made-it-to-netflix-zimbabwes-cook-off/</ref>.  Ni filime ya kabiri ya Zimbabwe yitabiriwe n’amahanga nyuma ya ''Neria''<ref>https://thisisafrica.me/arts-and-culture/netflix-cookoff-an-authentically-zimbabwean-film/</ref> .  Iyi filime irashimwa nka imwe muri filime nziza kurusha izindi zose muri Sinema ya Zimbabwe nyuma ya ''Neria'' na yellow Card kandi yafunguwe ku buryo bwiza cyane bwatanzwe n'Abanyazimbabwe<ref>https://www.africavivre.com/zimbabwe/a-voir/films/cook-off-conte-zimbabween-a-8000.html</ref>. Iyi filime izwiho gusenya imyumvire y’inganda za firime zo muri Zimbabwe zari zamugaye kubera ibibazo by’ubukungu ndetse na hyperinflation muri iki gihugu.<ref>https://summary.org/netflix-zimbabwe-cook-off-comedy/</ref> 

== Inyandiko ==
Iyo umubyeyi urera abana wenyine Anesu ( Tendaiishe Chitima ) yinjiye rwihishwa mu marushanwa yo guteka kuri tereviziyo n’umuhungu we, agomba gutsinda ibyo nyina atemera ndetse no guhangana n’abatetsi babigize umwuga.<ref>https://www.africanvibes.com/cook-off-lifts-zimbabwe-film-industry-onto-the-global-stage-2/</ref>

