== Gutanga ibihembo ==
Filime yakiriye ibihembo bike yanatoranijwe mubirori bya firime<ref>https://www.newsday.co.zw/2020/05/cook-off-set-for-netflix/</ref>. Yatwaye ibihembo bine byose mu birori bya firime, harimo bibiri buri kimwe mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cambria 2020<ref>https://www.chronicle.co.zw/cook-off-to-show-on-zbctv/</ref>. na [[Zimbabwe]] International Film Festival.   Iyi filime kandi yahawe ibihembo bibiri by’ubuhanzi byatanzwe n’inama y’ubuhanzi ya Zimbabwe muri 2019<ref>https://www.senscritique.com/film/Cook_Off/42318750</ref>.

